INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Sauza Reposado',750,25.36,650,14.00,'https://proxy.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.thewhiskyexchange.com%2F900%2Fteqla_sau18.jpg&f=1','A premium Reposado from Sauza, this is aged in American white oak barrels for four months, offering a mellow, spicy, sweet flavor.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Sauza Conmemorativo',750,25.36,650,14.50,'http://cdn2.bigcommerce.com/server5500/tpbc2s65/products/647/images/680/sauza_anejo_conmemorativo750_new__38726__91709.1358534100.1280.1280.jpg','Dry fruit and agave nectar notes. Sweet toasted oak touch increases aromatic complexity.  Highlighted sweetness, mild tannins, lightly sweet toasted oak and vanilla with mild astringency.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Sauza Hornitos',750,25.36,650,12.50,'https://proxy.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcbo.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Flcbo%2Fproducts%2F143040.jpg%2Fjcr%3Acontent%2Frenditions%2Fcq5dam.web.1280.1280.jpeg&f=1','Fine agave, herbal & green apple notes.  Balanced agave with apple & herbal notes, slightly woody.  Medium to full-bodied spirit with warm, slightly astringent finish.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Fortaleza Reposado',750,25.36,668,12.00,'https://dandm.com/image/cache/215182_11-700x1000.jpg','Exotic citrus, popcorn, earthy caramel, wood spice, rich agave, orchard fruit, complex herbal notes. Really top stuff.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Fortaleza Blanco',750,25.36,668,13.00,'https://cdna2.zoeysite.com/Adzpo594RQGDpLcjBynL1z/cache=expiry:31536000/compress/https://s3.amazonaws.com/zcom-media/sites/a0iE000000B0omIIAR/media/catalog/product/f/o/fortalezablanco_base_4.jpg','Everything a good tequila should be with herbaceous, vegetal agave, citrus, green olives and brine as well as a creaminess that carries into rich buttery character.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Fortaleza Anejo',1000,33.81,668,12.00,'http://tequilafortaleza.com/media/fortaleza-anejo.jpg','A beautiful combination of agave and butterscotch, sultana and mixed peels. Oily, complex, outstanding.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Don Julio Blanco',750,25.36,637,14.00,'http://www.dateeats.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Don-Julio-silver.jpg','Citrussy and fresh, Don Julio\'s Blanco tequila was rated as \"Classic\" by Wine Enthusiast Magazine. This is their highest commendation, and it was awarded after their noted critic, F Paul Pacult after he tasted over 250 spirits.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Don Julio Reposado',1000,33.81,637,13.00,'http://www.drinkspirits.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/reposado.jpg','Barrel aged for 8 months. Soft lemon and fruit aromas on the nose followed by delicate hit of spice. Very soft on the palate with vanilla and cinnamon mixing well. Sweet ending.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Don Julio Anejo',1000,33.81,637,12.00,'http://cdn2.bigcommerce.com/server4900/7a906/products/945/images/1033/don-julio-anejo-750__26643.1335464513.1280.1280.jpg','A fresh blend of lime, grapefruit and mandarin citrus aromas with a rich touch of caramel.  Full-bodied and complex with expressions of cooked agave, wild honey and oak-infused butterscotch.  Bright and lightly spiced finish with the essence of wild honey.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Don Julio 1942',1000,33.81,712,15.00,'https://www.wallywine.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/1800x/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/0/4/040335.jpg','Rich caramel and chocolate.  Warm oak, vanilla and roasted agave.  Lingering oak and rich vanilla.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Casa Noble Crystal',1000,33.81,665,12.00,'http://professorcocktail.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Casa-Noble-Crystal-Tequila.jpg','The clean, crisp taste of our Blanco tequila celebrates the fresh flavor of the noble Blue Weber Agave. Enticing aromas set the palate for flavors of honey, buttery-sweet cooked agave and a hint of citrus. Triple distilled for a well-balanced and smoother-than-glass finish, this Blanco is in a class by itself.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Casa Noble Reposado',750,25.36,665,13.00,'https://www.abc.virginia.gov/library/product-images/2018-02-15/casa-noble-tequila-reposado.jpg?h=400&w=400&la=en&hash=2DE961865DE31723D145BD57F9C6B00880F27511','Aromas of vanilla, lemongrass, and floral notes are balanced with flavors of sweet cooked agave and toasted oak. Aged for 364 days in French white oak barrels (other Reposados are aged for four–six months).','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Tequila','Casa Noble Anejo',750,25.36,665,15.00,'https://spiritedgifts.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/a/casa_noble_anejo.jpg','Patience is the secret ingredient of our acclaimed Añejo. Aged for a full two years in French white oak barrels, the complex aromas of dried fruits and spice complement flavors of toasted oak, butterscotch, vanilla, and sweet cooked agave.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Amaro','Fernet Branca',750,25.36,605,14.00,'https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/900/vermo_fer13.jpg','Nose: Marmalade, hints of fresh mint and pepper. Very aromatic.  Palate: Perfumed notes of potpourri, fruits, peppermint and zest. Rich.  Finish: Dry, oaky finish. Very herbal.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Amaro','Amargo Valet',750,25.36,700,15.00,'https://img.thewhiskyexchange.com/540/liq_ama20.jpg','Vallet Amargo Angostura is a 90 Proof bitter liqueur made from Angostura bark and a maceration of cherry fruits, cloves and other roots and spices. Herbal notes of bittersweet dark chocolate and citrus rind balance an earthly richness to create this delightful elixir.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Amaro','Amaro Nonino',750,25.36,703,14.00,'http://www.lcbo.com/content/dam/lcbo/products/933796.jpg/jcr:content/renditions/cq5dam.web.1280.1280.jpeg','The opening pass is like an open market for mountain herbs, flowers, and spices. The midpalate explodes with herbal/rooty/floral tastes including dried fruit, fruit peel, quinine, cassia bark, and fruit stone.','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
INSERT INTO `Alcohol` (`type`,`brandStyle`,`sizeML`,`sizeOZ`,`emptyBottleWeight`,`gramsPerOunce`,`image`,`tastingNotes`,`createdAt`,`updatedAt`) VALUES ('Amaro','Cynar',750,25.36,688,16.00,'https://www.drinksupermarket.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/c/y/cynar-artichoke-liqueur-70cl_temp.jpg','The artichoke liqueur known for its versatility and taste Cynar is an artichoke based bitter. Its distinctive flavour is enriched from an infusion of 13 herbs and plants, making it a completely natural drink, rich in scents and a unique taste . It perfectly conserves all the health properties of the ingredients used in its preparation. Only moderately alcoholic (16.5%) Cynar is a modern and versatile drink that is always welcome','2019-04-05 17:14:57','2019-04-05 17:14:57');
